name: Mark-Inducil-Dreamweaver-NFT-335
description:
Our ego is usually associated with
hubris or vanity however the ego is
really our perception of ourselves
within our personal reality. Everyone
has an ego with their own sets of
delusions and hard truths that they
live with. I wanted to create a piece
that would symbolise all the changes
our egos undertake throughout our
lives. The numerous breakdowns and
breakthroughs that we go through
and the various changes we
experience in order to either protect
or rebuild the way we see ourselves.
